      <h3 class="title">
      <a href="/article/8160#comment-328410" class="active">i have an old ipod,</a>          </h3>
  
  
  <div class="picture">
  <img src="/files/linuxjournal.com/images/personicon.jpg" alt="Anonymous&#039;s picture" title="Anonymous&#039;s picture"  /></div>

  <div class="submitted">
    Submitted by Anonymous (not verified) on Tue, 11/11/2008 - 22:18.  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>i have an old ipod, formatted for mac &amp; when i try to use the program it can't transfer any files to the ipod, and it gives me a "read-only" system error message any tips? i've tried restoring it on a mac &amp; using other methods like transfering them on rythynmbox via the menus and such, the wierd thing is i can bring files over from the ipod but not vice-a-versa.</p>
      </div>

  
