      <h3 class="title">
      <a href="/article/8160#comment-211315" class="active">Compliment</a>          </h3>
  
  
  <div class="picture">
  <img src="/files/linuxjournal.com/images/personicon.jpg" alt="John Turner&#039;s picture" title="John Turner&#039;s picture"  /></div>

  <div class="submitted">
    Submitted by John Turner (not verified) on Tue, 01/16/2007 - 12:56.  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>This is the best information I have found for a newbie like me on the web. Keep up the good work!</p>
      </div>

  
</div></div> <!-- /comment-inner, /comment -->
