<div class="indented"><a id="comment-135892"></a>
<div class="comment comment-published even comment-by-anon"><div class="comment-inner clear-block">

      <h3 class="title">
      <a href="/article/8160#comment-135892" class="active">My Ipod shuffle charges on a</a>          </h3>
  
  
  <div class="picture">
  <img src="/files/linuxjournal.com/images/personicon.jpg" alt="Anonymous&#039;s picture" title="Anonymous&#039;s picture"  /></div>

  <div class="submitted">
    Submitted by Anonymous (not verified) on Fri, 04/14/2006 - 16:43.  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>My Ipod shuffle charges on a USB 2.0 port.  I've tried both the 1 Gig (I bought that) and 512MB (free from bankone).  Make sure you format it FAT32 via a windoze machine</p>
      </div>

  
