<div class="indented"><a id="comment-209428"></a>
<div class="comment comment-published odd comment-by-anon"><div class="comment-inner clear-block">

      <h3 class="title">
      <a href="/article/8160#comment-209428" class="active">You don&#039;t need windows to</a>          </h3>
  
  
  <div class="picture">
  <img src="/files/linuxjournal.com/images/personicon.jpg" alt="synorgy&#039;s picture" title="synorgy&#039;s picture"  /></div>

  <div class="submitted">
    Submitted by synorgy (not verified) on Sun, 01/07/2007 - 19:25.  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>You don't need windows to format an iPod. Install gParted, plug in your  iPod and fire up gParted. It will open and (once you change the device) allow you to format your iPod (or your harddrive if you aren't careful)</p>
      </div>

  
</div></div> <!-- /comment-inner, /comment -->
